articles.title: TCS, Transamerica end $2 billion contract due to macro environment - The Economic Times
articles.description: Indian information technology (IT) company Tata Consultancy Services said on Friday it has mutually agreed with insurance provider Transamerica to end a $2 billion contract, citing reasons including a challenging macro environment.

articles.title: An American tourist has died following an attack near Germany’s Neuschwanstein Castle - CNN
articles.description: A 21-year-old American woman died after being assaulted and pushed down a slope by an American man near one of Germany’s most popular tourist sights, Neuschwanstein Castle, in Bavaria, according to local police.
